      "content": "Okay, $45,000 makes more sense. Look, with the new quantum processor upgrades we're planning for next quarter, we're actually going to need every cent we can get. If we return this to the central pool now, they'll just reallocate it to the BioTech lab and we won't see it again. \n\nIs there any way we can justify keeping this surplus in our operating budget for the next cycle instead of returning it? Maybe as an emergency contingency fund for equipment maintenance or something?",
